com.threerings.nexus.distrib
Interface Keyed

public interface Keyed

An interface that must be implemented by keyed entities. Keyed entities are registered in tables shared across all server nodes in a Nexus network, and can be addressed from any server node in the network.

Method Summary
 Comparable<?> getKey()
          Returns the globally unique key for this instance (must be a primitive or String).
